data.description: Welcome Home to this like-new Pueblo West beauty! Situated on over an acre of land, this ranch style home features main level living at its finest.. The open concept great room/kitchen area is perfect for entertaining.. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, an island perfect for counter stools, a whole home water filtration system, and toe warmers underneath the sink - talk about luxury.. Down the hall, you can enter the mud room/laundry area that leads to the oversized 3 car garage.. As you continue down the hall, you'll find 2 large guest bedrooms, storage closet holding the water filtration system, and a full bathroom that also features the incredible under-sink toe warmers.. Finish at the end of the hall with the huge master bedroom with large walk-in closet and a 5 piece bathroom (yes, with under-sink toe warmers!) featuring a free standing shower, double vanity, and large soaking tub.. Look no further, once you check this one out, you'll know you found the one!
